<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Beltline </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Renowned for its electrifying nightlife, eclectic mix of restaurants and metropolitan
                culture, the Beltline is also one of the most highly desirable residential neighborhoods for
                homebuyers and investors alike. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Beltline comprise a variety of housing options including single family
                detached units as well as high rise apartment condominiums that are available at an average price of
                around $430,000. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Home to some of Calgaryâ€™s most popular destinations, Beltline is ideal for energetic
                people who enjoy the fast-paced lifestyle of the modern times.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Uptown 17th is a popular and dense mix of bars,restaurants, nightclubs, and boutique
                shops, Nicknamed the "Red Mile" during the Stanley Cup playoffs in 2004. During this time, you would
                regularly see over tens of thousands of fans partying along 17th Ave with its bars and pubs on game
                nights.</p>

        </div>
